  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507590/extras/009165e798ae52b75272fa65b5fbbc0d.poster.avif?t=1773460224\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507590/extras/009165e798ae52b75272fa65b5fbbc0d.webm?t=1773460224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507590/extras/009165e798ae52b75272fa65b5fbbc0d.mp4?t=1773460224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Mouse Game</strong> is a hardcore \"mouse maze\" game where you avoid deadly traps to secure the cheese. Run, dodge, and weave your way through 35 increasingly difficult levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PERSONALIZE</strong> your mouse with dozens of unlockable colors and accessories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLOCK</strong> a diverse range of rewarding achievements! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHALLENGE</strong> your skills with 5 unique gameplay-altering challenge modes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMPROVE</strong> your best attempts with faster completions! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONQUER</strong> the impossible by beating all 35 levels with all 5 challenges enabled! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507590/extras/aba1f40a41fe5675e7f72f6c0d7153c8.poster.avif?t=1773460224\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507590/extras/aba1f40a41fe5675e7f72f6c0d7153c8.webm?t=1773460224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507590/extras/aba1f40a41fe5675e7f72f6c0d7153c8.mp4?t=1773460224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
